reviewText: Good quality discs and a good value.
Great collection!  One disc was bad and would not play.  Vendor replaced at no cost.  I am a happy camper.
love Sandra Bullock and these DVD's  work great
The DVDs are excellent ,shipping was prompt
daughter loved it.  great stocking stuffer.
nice collection of Sandra Bullock for nice price!

Hum,  Miss Congeniality skips so badly it's barely watchable, so that was a waste.  I'm thinking it's the packaging, nothing between any of the disc's to protect them.  Second disc, Miss Congeniality 2, skipped a bit, but fast forwarding and backing up seems to have relieved that.  Haven't watched the other three yet.  Should have been a good buy.  Not so much so far though.
